IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
PROGRAM-ID. PI-Calculation-Steve28.

DATA DIVISION.
WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
01 i BINARY-LONG VALUE 1.
01 n BINARY-LONG.
01 PI1 PIC S9(1)V9(10) VALUE 0.0.
01 PI2 PIC S9(1)V9(10) VALUE 0.0.

PROCEDURE DIVISION.
ACCEPT n.
PERFORM VARYING i FROM 1 BY 1 UNTIL i > n
    COMPUTE PI1 = PI1 + 1/(i*i)
    COMPUTE PI2 = PI2 - (-1)**i/(-1 + 2*i)
END-PERFORM
COMPUTE PI1 = (PI1*6)**.5
COMPUTE PI2 = PI2*4
DISPLAY PI1.
DISPLAY PI2.
STOP RUN.
